| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0859 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 86b63afa-3a40-58a2-8a11-9d3e3d45a75d"
